snippet.title: Holiday Party: Mascot Brawl - Game Trailer 3
snippet.description: A silly multiplayer party game, Holiday Party brings festive cheer year-round with battles and mini-games matched with absurd weapons. Compete against friends while roasting them with a flamethrower and slapping them with a GIANT FISH. Jump into this hilarious holiday-themed brawling mayhem today!
